 
div
  .box#bundle-bowsette
    .tile.is-ancestor.is-marginless
      .tile.is-parent.is-vertical.is-4
        .tile.is-child
          a.delete.is-large.is-hidden-desktop.delbdl(data-del="bundle-bowsette")
          div.is-hidden-desktop
              .title: b  Special Bundle
              .subtitle.is-5 Bowsette Deluxe Pack
          img(src="/images/bowsettedeluxe.png")
      .tile.is-parent.is-vertical.is-8.is-marginless
        .tile.is-child.small
          .level
            .level-left: div.is-hidden-mobile
              .title: b  Special Bundle
              .subtitle.is-5 Bowsette Deluxe Pack
            .level-item
            .level-right
              a.delete.is-large.is-hidden-mobile.delbdl(style="margin-top: -60px !important;" data-del="bundle-bowsette")
          hr
          p
           | Join the Bowsette hype and get all her cosmetics at once!
           | This pack includes all Bowsette BGs available in the store + 2 Exclusive-Rare options, as well as a cute Bowsette sticker!
          //r

        .columns
          .column
            p 
              b This bundle contains:
              ul 
                li • 8 x UR Backgrounds
                li • 2 x SR Backgrounds
                li • 2 x XR Backgrounds
                li • 1 x XR Sticker

          .column
            .level-item
            .level-right: div
              p.subtitle.is-marginless
                img(src="/images/rubine.png" width="25px")
                span <b>383 021</b> Rubines
              p.subtitle.is-marginless
                img(src="/images/jade.png" width="25px")
                span <b>7 229 138</b> Jades
              p.subtitle.is-marginless
                img(src="/images/sapphire.png" width="25px")
                span <b>128</b> Sapphires
    .level
      //.level-left.small.help
        p.small: i This Bundle is a "custom feature" from a donator's <b>Palladium+ reward</b>, offered by <a href="/profile/134726089237856256">Dizzy#3333</a>
      .level-item
