            .r: .button.buybundle(currency="rubine" data-cost=383021 data-item="bowsettebundle") Take my Rubines!
            .j: .button.button.buybundle(currency="jade" data-cost=7229138 data-item="bowsettebundle") Take my Jades!
            .s: .button.buybundle(currency="sapphire" data-cost=128 data-item="bowsettebundle") Take my Sapphires!


